<html>
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="content-type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
    <r:layoutResources/>
    <title>Search criteria</title>
  </head>
  <body>
  	<div id="main"> 
    <g:form url='[controller: "search", action: "criteria"]' id="searchCriteria" name="searchCriteria" method="get">
    	<p>Before we show you some results, we want to know more about what you're looking for.</p>
    	<p>Imagine that someone else is reviewing the results on your behalf. 
    	In the box below, provide as much detail as possible about the item(s) you're searching for and 
    	any criteria that you would use to determine whether a result it relevant or not.
    	</p>
    </g:form>
  	</div>
  </body>
</html>
